oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Brad Paisley at the Sommet Center
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Paisley, Brad; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (green and blue - green on white) announcing the Bonfires and Amplifiers Tour starring Brad Paisley with Rodney Atkins and Chuck Wicks at the Bridgestone Arena (formerly the Sommet Center) on February 15. Poster features woodcuts of flames and a microphone.
